      <title>拉加德不愿降息 市场对欧洲央行下一步举措充满猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/lagarde-s-reluctant-cut-leaves-markets-guessing-on-next-ecb-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行兑现了降息承诺，但同时表示通胀率要花更长时间才能达到 2%，这让投资者对下一步政策走向不解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/lagarde-s-reluctant-cut-leaves-markets-guessing-on-next-ecb-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:13:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将迎来高温天气 玉米价格三周内涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/corn-jumps-most-in-three-weeks-with-us-set-for-heat-wave</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国新兴作物即将面临首次高温威胁，芝加哥玉米价格一度上涨 2.8%，创下自 5 月 10 日以来的最大盘中涨幅。]]></description>
