    <item>
      <title>银行利用复杂的抵押贷款产品来应对存款流失风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/banks-tap-complex-mortgage-product-to-fight-deposit-flight-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在高利率环境下，银行为了应对存款损失的风险越来越大，正在加大对抵押贷款债券市场中提供短期证券的复杂部分的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/banks-tap-complex-mortgage-product-to-fight-deposit-flight-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:07:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦开始降低利率，与欧洲央行降息四分之一个百分点保持一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/denmark-starts-easing-rates-matches-ecb-s-quarter-point-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦央行与欧元区其他国家央行同步下调基准利率 25 个基点，以捍卫其与欧元的挂钩政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/denmark-starts-easing-rates-matches-ecb-s-quarter-point-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 15:00:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行官员几乎排除 7 月降息的可能性，9 月降息前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/ecb-officials-all-but-rule-out-july-cut-with-september-unclear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧洲央行官员几乎排除了7月份第二次降息的可能性，一些官员还质疑在9月份的下次会议上采取此举是否明智。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/ecb-officials-all-but-rule-out-july-cut-with-september-unclear</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 14:46:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
